attributes.title: A RACE FOR SLUGS - GTAV: Overtime Rumble
attributes.description: The AH crew is switching up the teams and using their striking strategy to get the most points as possible, until they find a map which rewards being slow.

attributes.title: Lindsay Wins Again - GTA V
attributes.description: You heard that right, we're playing Lindsay Wins again! The rules: Lindsay must get 1st place in a GTA V transform race, if you pass Lindsay you have to stop, and if you touch her you have to go to last place. The only person who wins in this terrible and chaotic game of chicken, is Lindsay.

attributes.title: G.T. Aliens - GTA V
attributes.description: The boys are equipped with the fancy new Up-n-Atomizer rayguns, and hold on -  is that an alien? Everyone is blasting off in more ways than one in these extraterrestrial airport games.

attributes.title: WE DON'T NEED TO FINISH - GTA V: Jack Bag 6
attributes.description: We're back with 5 more curated Rockstar maps in Jack's little sack.

attributes.title: GEOFF'S GOLDEN TICKET - GTA V | Let's Play
attributes.description: We're placing a bounty on Geoff in a public lobby, and it's up to the rest of the crew to keep him safe for 24 hours. Will anyone be able to steal Geoff's golden ticket?

attributes.title: PULLING A BANKSY - GTA V: Deciphering Geoff (#2)
attributes.description: We picked a number between 1 and 14 of Geoff's notebook, and now the boys are put to the challenge of creating an art piece on top of the Maze Bank Tower. But wait, why are there so many men with knives waiting on the street? Tune in to see the insanity of episode 2 of Deciphering Geoff.

attributes.title: TINY TERRORS - GTA V
attributes.description: These tiny RC cars have a taste for human flesh, crazy explosions, and tiny sumo.

attributes.title: THE LAZER JOB - GTA V Heist
attributes.description: In dire need of that sweet moolah, the Fake AH Crew attempts to pull off a new, homemade heist! Can they successfully steal a Lazer, or will their plans go south like they always do?

attributes.title: STUFFING THE BABUSHKA - GTA V
attributes.description: The airport boys have tried to shove just about everything into a titan, but now they've gotten themselves a babushka, and they're going to stuff it like a thanksgiving turkey. What will fit? Find out!

attributes.title: GEOFF WINS - GTA V
attributes.description: Jack hand-picked 5 rockstar maps for another Jack Bag, but wait. Something is fishy here. This isn't a normal Jack Bag!

attributes.title: BOMSTA LA VISTA - GTA V
attributes.description: The Fake AH Crew is playing Bomsta-la-vista, a game where bomber jets try to take down a half track before it makes to the capture point. Strap in for some cinematic chaos.

attributes.title: WE'RE FEELIN' BIPPY - GTA V - Snipers Vs Stunters
attributes.description:
It's Snipers Vs Stunters and everyone is feeling "bippy." Which team is crazy enough to be the last one standing?
Check out our new merch: https://store.roosterteeth.com/collections/achievement-hunter

attributes.title: THE SIDE GIG - GTA V Heist Lite
attributes.description: The boys haven't been bringing in enough cash from their usual heists, so Ryan set them up with a side gig. They have to kill five guys in seven minutes, and they have to plan it all on the fly. The simplest plans are the best, right?

attributes.title: Snack Heist - GTA V: Heist
attributes.description: After multiple failed heist attempts, the Fake AH crew is very broke. To get some cash, Jeremy contructs a heist that's so easy, the crew just has to be successful. It also has the added bonus of snacks!

attributes.title: CAR FIGHTS AND STROBE LIGHTS - GTA V: Offense Defense
attributes.description: We're playing Offense Defense and there's more than tactical planning in this episode... much more.

attributes.title: HATE LOOPS AND PANIC HORNS - GTA V: Deadline
attributes.description: It's our annual Deadline GTA! Join us for some Tron bikes, power-ups, chaotic crashes, and odd British accents.

attributes.title: SONIC THE HEDGEHOG THE MOVIE - GTA V | Let's Play
attributes.description: Sonic and friends are gonna go REALLY REALLY FAST in order to beat Dr. Robotnik in a race to get all of the chaos emeralds so Sonic can go super saiyan. Yes, that's canon.

attributes.title: WE HAVE TO KILL YOUR WIFE - GTA V: Jack Bag 7
attributes.description: Jack's reached into his bag, and picked out four new maps. There's some BMX, bumper cars, wall rides, and dixie rect.

attributes.description:

attributes.description:
Thanks to Stuber for sponsoring this video. Check out the movie out on 7/12: https://www.foxmovies.com/movies/stuber.
We're picking up our friend Kumail Nanjiani for a relaxing Sunday drive in GTA V: Online. We tell stories, mug Gavin, chase trains and have an overall chill time.
